      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't have the time for the clinic right now. like, if i just use some over the counter ear drops to soften the wax, would that be a safe way to handle it at home instead of going in? i'm pretty sure it's just the wax being pushed in so i should be fine if i just treat it myself, right?",
